                     <interp inst="t17300828-32-person182" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             depos'd, That the former Evidence crying out a Highwayman, he pursued him till he quitted his Horse, and said, he would shoot any Body that should offer to lay hold on him; but a Man got behind him, and seiz'd him.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="173008280010"></xptr>Parrot Fenton , depos'd, That when the Prisoner was before the Justice, he would not tell his Name, saying, if he were 
