            , no Body should know who he was.</p>
               <p>The Prisoner had nothing to say in his Defence, but to ask the Prosecutor, If he did not lend him his Horse? The Prosecutor reply'd, Not willingly, but if he did borrow him, it was with Pistol in Hand; the Fact being plainly prov'd, the Jury found him <rs id="t17300828-32-verdict175" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17300828-32-verdict175" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
